'''Alfriston''' is a small suburb of [[Auckland]], [[New Zealand]]'s largest city. Prior to November 2010 it was under the authority of the Papakura District Council and is now part of the enlarged Auckland city. Alfriston has one secondary school, [[Alfriston College]]. The suburb is in the '''Franklin''' ward, one of the thirteen administrative divisions of Auckland City.
